    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "> **Security Tip**: It is not recommended to change `LISTEN_ADDR` to `0.0.0.0:7000` to expose directly to the public network, as the management panel has no authentication protection. For external access, please use an SSH tunnel or configure an authenticated reverse proxy (such as Nginx + Basic Auth)."
